name: Winter Inspired Happy New Year Postcard Set
description:
Set with 4 different cards: 3 - winter plants, 1 - Happy New Year card. Inspired by Christams mood, winter plants and simple style of retro postcards. A perfect cards for a New Year celebration. Illustration printed on watercolor paper and is paired with a soft white envelope. Limited edition. 

- Size:  14 sm x 10 sm 
- Set with 4 cards
- Blank interior
- Matching white envelope
- Printed locally in Bangkok by awesome people
- Printed full color on natural white watercolor paper
